General.Name: Mithril Resources Ltd
General.Description: Mithril Resources Limited engages in the exploration and development of mineral properties in Mexico and Australia. It explores for gold, silver, zinc, and nickel deposits. The company primarily holds interest in the Copalquin Gold Silver project covering an area of 70 square kilometres located in the Durango State, Mexico. It also holds interests in the Billy Hills Zinc, Kurnalpi, Lignum Dam, and Limestone Well projects located in Australia. The company was incorporated in 2002 and is based in Melbourne, Australia.
